trscore, trspprint, trsdsl

Types

AstKind = enum
  akStrLit, akIntLit, akIdent, akCall, akCondition
Ast = object
  case kind*: AstKind
  of akStrLit, akIdent:
      strVal*: string

  of akIntLit:
      intVal*: int

  else:
      subnodes*: seq[Ast]

  
AstTerm = Term[Ast, AstKind]

Lets

astImpl = TermImpl[Ast, AstKind](getSym: proc (n: Ast): AstKind = result = n.kind, isFunctorSym: proc (
    kind: AstKind): bool = result = contains({akCall..akCondition}, kind), makeFunctor: proc (
    op: AstKind; sub: seq[Ast]): Ast =
  result = Ast(kind: op)
  result.subnodes = sub, getArguments: proc (n: Ast): seq[Ast] = result = n.subnodes, valStrGen: proc (
    n: Ast): string = result = exprRepr(n))
